{"tid":1317492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一哥被屌】盧偉聰強烈譴責暴力行為 市民粗口回應","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T10:16:06.000Z","uid":39092,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f160f0a06afad719375aed45c560362397d35638","tid":1317492,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:32.000Z","msg":"【02:35】一哥盧偉聰表示，昨晚清場時拘捕逾40人，包括涉嫌非法集結及襲警等罪行，強調對暴力行為予以最強烈譴責，會全力調查，追究到底。盧偉聰又表示，事件中多名警員受傷送院，包括一名警員手指斷裂、一名警員臉骨及眼骨爆裂、一名警員遭高空擲物擊中腹部。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而在盧偉聰向傳媒講話時，有示威者向盧偉聰講粗口。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市廣場爆發警民衝突，導致多名警員受傷，凌晨約1時30分，警務處處長盧偉聰到達大埔那打素醫院，探望受傷警員。<br />\n<br />\n另外醫管局表示，截至凌晨零時半，有22人受傷送院，包括14男8女，其中3人情況嚴重，18人情況穩定，另1人已出院。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人昨晚表示，昨日下午和平示威遊行結束後，有部分示威者故意堵塞道路，以暴力襲擊警察，並肆意破壞社會安寧。政府對這些違法行為，予以強烈譴責，又指法治是香港的基石，社會絕不容忍這些暴力行為。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190715/59824468?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2rHc-1e62ajdBkkCoQ3FGU3QHXh3ZEvLzweCPm4q1mvIvVzyfnYe7yYAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F59824468%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2rHc-1e62ajdBkkCoQ3FGU3QHXh3ZEvLzweCPm4q1mvIvVzyfnYe7yYAw&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=1eaca86f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F59824468%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2rHc-1e62ajdBkkCoQ3FGU3QHXh3ZEvLzweCPm4q1mvIvVzyfnYe7yYAw&h=44d1af8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190715/59824468?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2rHc-1e62ajdBkkCoQ3FGU3QHXh3ZEvLzweCPm4q1mvIvVzyfnYe7yYAw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb258d5e71954e7e97a03bdbb7368cfa6a610167","tid":1317492,"uid":35613,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉聰你含撚啦屌你老母，扮傻</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a2cf197e62f86a7f7a03e9d347688744a6bdb9","tid":1317492,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:58:04.000Z","msg":"咩時間講，想睇"},{"pid":"e55d44463d57a2b8c256703b2432062188d90f14","tid":1317492,"uid":35613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a2cf197e62f86a7f7a03e9d347688744a6bdb9","tid":1317492,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:58:04.000Z","msg":"咩時間講，想睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:00:53.000Z","msg":"7：59"},{"pid":"5dfcbe23276eb783383be33ceb97c4b73fb4b533","tid":1317492,"uid":193056,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/596896340490193/posts/1315126888667131/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F596896340490193%2Fposts%2F1315126888667131%2F&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=c9061492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/596896340490193/posts/1315126888667131/<